###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/AirOutlet
copi:AirOutlet rdf:type owl:Class ;
               rdfs:subClassOf <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/MaterialArtifact> ;
               rdfs:label "air outlet"@en ,
