                  rdfs:label "flow control function"@en ;
                  annotation:isPrimitive "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
                  annotation:naturalLanguageDefinition "An identity-giving designed function realized in a FlowControl process; the function of modulating, regulating, or blocking fluid flow through a conduit or vessel connection."@en ;
                  annotation:primitiveRationale "OWL gives only necessary conditions; the some+only pair characterises the function for inference."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/COPI_0000027
